          },
          "reviewBody": "International Public School offers a comprehensive educational experience with dedicated teachers and a vibrant learning atmosphere. Notably, the music classes shine, earning a commendable 4.5/5 rating. However, there are areas for improvement. The limited emphasis on physical activity suggests a need for a more balanced approach to enhance student well-being. Teacher dedication is evident, yet there's room for growth in knowledge depth, earning a 3/5 rating. Similarly, the washroom facilities, rated 3/5, require attention for an enhanced overall experience. Constructive feedback aims at continuous improvement, ensuring a holistic and enriching environment. By addressing these aspects, International Public School can further elevate its educational setting, providing a more comfortable and well-rounded experience for students and staff.",
